Di mana?

94
00:07:11,690 --> 00:07:13,000
Aku sudah tahu.

95
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:19,390
Detektif Yoon, coba lihat ini!

96
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:23,630
Apa itu?

97
