214
00:16:25,180 --> 00:16:26,650
Nama lengkap Kim Hee Yeon.

215
00:16:26,650 --> 00:16:27,750
<i>24 tahun.</i>

216
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:32,520
Pukul satu malam setelah selesai
acara kumpul bersama Perkumpulan Busan,

217
00:16:32,890 --> 00:16:34,880
